# Architecture Decision Records

> ⚠️ **Stub — Phase 1.**

Each ADR captures one decision in Nygard format. Use
`/cadence-adr <title>` to create a new one.

## Format

```
# ADR-NNNN — <title>

## Status
Accepted | Superseded by ADR-NNNN | Deprecated

## Context
What's the situation forcing this decision?

## Decision
What did we decide? One sentence, then specifics.

## Consequences
What does this make easier? Harder?

## Trigger
What prompted writing this ADR? (Usually a retrospective entry.)
```

## Numbering

Monotonic. Never reuse a number.

